sources.title: The Naked Street (restored, with intro and outro commentary) (1955, film noir, imdb score: 6.5)
sources.description: The Naked Street is a 1955 American crime film noir directed by Maxwell Shane . The drama features Farley Granger , Anthony Quinn and Anne Bancroft in a story about an enforcer who tries to control his sister's life by falsely clearing her boyfriend of murder.
